trans-unit.source: Creates and populates an <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTable"></xref> that is used by the <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.MetadataStore"></xref> to provide attribute lookup and registration.
trans-unit.target: Skapar och fyller i en <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTable"> </xref> som används av den <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.MetadataStore"> </xref> för attributsökning och registrering.

trans-unit.source: Use <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.AddCallback%2A>, <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.AddCustomAttributes%2A>, and <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.AddTable%2A> to populate the builder, then call <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.CreateTable%2A> to acquire an <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTable> containing the desired collection of attributes.
trans-unit.target: Använd <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.AddCallback%2A>, <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.AddCustomAttributes%2A>, och <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.AddTable%2A>för att fylla i builder anropa <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.CreateTable%2A>att erhålla ett <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTable>som innehåller den önskade samlingen attribut.</xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTable> </xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.CreateTable%2A> </xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.AddTable%2A> </xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.AddCustomAttributes%2A> </xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.AddCallback%2A>

trans-unit.source: Creates a new instance of the <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Skapar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: Specifies a callback that will be invoked when metadata for the given type is needed.
trans-unit.target: Anger ett återanrop som kommer att anropas när metadata för den angivna typen krävs.

trans-unit.source: The first time an <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTable> returned by <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.CreateTable%2A> is queried for attributes for `type`, `callback` is called to provide the metadata information.
trans-unit.target: Första gången en <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTable>returnerades av <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.CreateTable%2A>efterfrågas attribut för `type`, `callback` anropas för att tillhandahålla metadatainformationen.</xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.CreateTable%2A> </xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTable>

trans-unit.target: Typen som återanropet ger metadata.

trans-unit.source: If an attribute conflicts with another attribute already included in the builder, the last attribute added replaces previous attributes.
trans-unit.target: Om ett attribut står i konflikt med ett annat attribut som redan ingår i builder, ersätter den senaste attribut som läggs tidigare attribut.

trans-unit.source: Creates an attribute table that contains all of the attribute definitions provided through <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.AddCustomAttributes*> calls.
trans-unit.target: Skapar en tabell med attribut som innehåller alla attribut definitionerna via <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.AddCustomAttributes*>anrop.</xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.AddCustomAttributes*>

trans-unit.source: The table is a snapshot of the current state of the attribute builder; any attributes added by subsequent <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.AddCustomAttributes%2A> calls are not included in the table.
trans-unit.target: Tabellen är en ögonblicksbild av det aktuella tillståndet för attributet builder; alla attribut som läggs till av efterföljande <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.AddCustomAttributes%2A>anrop ingår inte i tabellen.</xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.AddCustomAttributes%2A>

trans-unit.source: If callback methods were used to declare attributes, those methods will not be evaluated during CreateTable.
trans-unit.target: Om callback-metoder som användes för att deklarera attribut, utvärderas dessa metoder inte under CreateTable.

trans-unit.source: Instead, the table will contain those callbacks and will evaluate them as needed.
trans-unit.target: Tabellen innehåller de återanrop i stället och utvärdera dem efter behov.

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTable"></xref> that can be passed to the metadata store.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTable"> </xref> som kan skickas till arkivet metadata.

trans-unit.source: Verifies that the attribute table that is being built contains valid attribute information.
trans-unit.target: Verifierar att attributtabellen som skapas innehåller information om giltiga attribut.

trans-unit.source: Some overrides of <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.AddCustomAttributes%2A>cannot validate that values passed to their parameters represent valid members on classes.
trans-unit.target: Vissa åsidosättningar av <xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.AddCustomAttributes%2A>kan inte verifiera att värden som skickas till deras parametrar representerar giltig medlemmar på klasser.</xref:System.Activities.Presentation.Metadata.AttributeTableBuilder.AddCustomAttributes%2A>

trans-unit.source: ValidateTable verifies that all custom attribute information corresponds to actual members.
trans-unit.target: ValidateTable verifierar att all information som attributet motsvarar faktiska medlemmar.

trans-unit.source: This method can take a long time to complete and is not recommended unless validation is explicitly needed.
trans-unit.target: Den här metoden kan ta lång tid att slutföra och rekommenderas inte såvida validering krävs explicit.

trans-unit.source: the state of the table is invalid.
